<p>We collect personal information that you provide to us, such as when you register for an account, contact us, or use certain features of our site. This may include:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Identification Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, etc.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you access and use our site, including IP addresses, device information, and browsing activity.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use the information we collect for various purposes, including:</p>
