</ul>

<h2>6. Your Data Rights</h2>
<p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. If you wish to exercise any of these rights, please contact us using the information below.</p>

<h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>Our services are not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child, we will take steps to remove it.</p>

<h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
